text: Weronika Biela (born 15 September 1991) is a Polish snowboarder. She competed in the 2013, 2015 and 2017 FIS Snowboard World Championships, and in the 2018 Winter Olympics, in parallel giant slalom. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Polish female snowboarders Category:Olympic snowboarders of Poland Category:Snowboarders at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zakopane Category:Universiade gold medalists for Poland Category:Universiade medalists in snowboarding Category:Competitors at the 2017 Winter Universiade
